ğŸ“ Project Structure

Key Features

Accounts Payable: Simulated end-to-end vendor payment management

Accounts Receivable: Automated invoice creation from contract-like inputs

AI Financial Copilot: GPT-powered assistant for invoice parsing and financial Q&A

Partner Pages: Simulated portals for Accounting and Developer partners

Core Technologies

Frontend

TypeScript, React, Next.js

Tailwind CSS, Shadcn for UI components

Chart.js / D3 for financial visualizations

Backend

Django (Python) or Ruby on Rails (alternative based on speed of development)

PostgreSQL

Auth0 for secure authentication

AI Integrations

OpenAI API (GPT-4) for invoice extraction & natural language queries

File upload & parsing for PDFs/images of invoices/contracts

DevOps

Deployed via Vercel (frontend) and Render/Fly.io/Heroku (backend)

GitHub Actions for CI/CD

ğŸ§  AI Use Case

AI Invoice Parser

Upload an invoice (PDF or image)

AI extracts key metadata (vendor, due date, amount, line items)

Pre-fills invoice form to simulate automation

AI Copilot (Chat Interface)

Ask "What are my top 3 recurring expenses this month?"

"How much did I spend on AWS last quarter?"

